<F P=101> Media Issues </F>
<H3> <TI>   Shumeyko To Meet Journalists </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0401202294 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel 
Network in Russian 1800 GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0401202294 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel 
Network </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Novosti" newscast] </F>
  [Text] It was reported today in the Russian Federation 
Press Committee that Government Chairman Viktor Chernomyrdin has 
instructed Vladimir Shumeyko to hold a meeting on 5 January with 
members of the journalists' strike committee to work out a 
solution to the problem which has arisen. A final decision will 
be taken within the next few days at a meeting between 
Chernomyrdin and the editors in chief of newspapers and 
magazines. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

