<H3> <TI>   Fighting Resumes in Nagorno-Karabakh 4 Jan </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0401124694 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 
1100 GMT 4 Jan 93 </F>

<F P=103> LD0401124694 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Russian Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Lur agency reports that Azerbaijani troops are 
sustaining losses in their offensive against Karabakh positions. 
According to the Nagorno-Karabakh army press service, 
Azerbaijan's losses numbered more than 90 men and officers. 
Combat operations resumed this morning in the north and 
northeast of the Nagorno- Karabakh Republic, where fierce 
fighting has been going on relentlessly for the last few days. 

</TEXT>

