<H3> <TI>   `Fierce Battles' Continue </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0501115894 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel 
Network in Russian 0600 GMT 5 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0501115894 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel 
Network </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Novosti" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Fierce battles are continuing in Nagorno-Karabakh 
between Azerbaijani formations and NKR [Nagorno-Karabakh 
Republic] forces. After intensive shelling, Azerbaijani troops 
have begun an offensive along the whole frontline from the Iraqi 
border [as heard] down to the Mrav Ridge [Crest] in the north of 
NKR's Mardakertskiy Rayon. There are casualties and fatalities 
on both sides. 
  Stepanakert has denied Baku's reports of the Azeri Army's 
successful capture of a number of settlements in the north 
section of the Karabakh front. 

</TEXT>

