<F P=102>  NC0401202894 Yerevan SNARK in English 1247 GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0401202894 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan SNARK </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tbilisi, January 4 (SNARK)--There created the joint 
commission on the regulation of the conflict in the Southern 
Ossetia. Aleksandr Kavsadze, Shevardnadze's representative in 
the conflict zones, told SNARK the commission will give the 
chance to organize the meetings with the participation of the 
Georgian, Southern Ossetian, Russian and the CSCE 
representatives. The conflict should be solved in two 
directions -- political and economic directions. The first task 
is to deliver food to the Georgian population of Southern 
Ossetia. 

</TEXT>

