<F P=103> LD0401195794 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi IBERIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Georgian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tbilisi, 4 Jan -- It has become known to Iberia that 
the forcible seizure of apartments belonging to Russian 
servicemen continues. In this connection the Russian Foreign 
Ministry strictly warns the Georgian authorities that if the 
Georgian Guard continues to forcibly occupy apartments belonging 
to Russian servicemen, then top Georgian political authorities 
will be made fully responsible for the possible consequences. 

