<F P=103> WS0501142994 </F>
<F P=104>  Minsk VO SLAVU RODINY </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by G. Palchevskiy: "One More Step Toward Unification </F>
of Left Forces"] 
  [Text] One more step toward the unification of left forces 
has been made in Grodno, where a unification plenum of the 
oblast branches of the Communist Party, the People's Movement of 
Belarus, the Movement for Democracy, Social Progress, and 
Justice [DSPS], was held. Following speeches on the 
socioeconomic situation in the Republic delivered by N. Prisada, 
K. Lisitsin, and S. Posokhov, secretaries of the Communist Party 
