<F P=100> CAUCASUS </F>
<F P=101> Armenia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Dram Drops Against Dollar </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0501184194 Yerevan SNARK in English 1234 GMT 5 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0501184194 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan SNARK </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yerevan, January 5 (SNARK)--The rate of Armenian 
dram relating to USD was dropped down 1/3 times [as received]. 
So, today, "Armimpexbank" (the Foreign Economic Bank) purchased 
USD for 100 drams and sold for 105 drams. 
  In the specialists' opinion the Armenian president's [word 
indistinct] about indexation of salaries, pensions and the 
resolution of the government to increase the prices for bread, 
transport, communal services influenced upon the rate. 
  The official rate, set by Central Bank of Armenia, equals 75 
drams for 1 USD. 

</TEXT>

