<H3> <TI>   Ambassador Shcherbak Meets With Israeli Opposition Leader </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0501132994 Kiev HOLOS UKRAYINY in Ukrainian 4 Jan 94 p 5 </F>
<F P=103> AU0501132994 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev HOLOS UKRAYINY </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "A Meeting With an Opposition Leader"] </F>
  [Text] Ukraine's Ambassador to Israel Yu. Shcherbak met 
with B. Netaniyahu, leader of the parliamentary opposition in 
the Knesset. During their conversation, the ambassador told him 
in detail about the political and economic situation in Ukraine. 
Yu. Shcherbak laid particular emphasis upon the issues of 
