  [Text] Lvov -- The [Lvov] region's procurator, Zenon Kotyk, 
informed a UNIAN correspondent today that his office has no 
official information about criminal proceedings instituted in 
the case of the sale by the region's state administration of the 
former missile base near Brody to Lvov's private firm Konza for 
