their confidential consultations on candidatures to the posts of 
speaker and his deputies have not yet reached agreement. 
INTERFAX has learned from a well-informed source that Russia's 
Choice, the Communists, the Agrarians, and the Liberal Democrats 
are ready to agree to the election of a speaker from one of the 
smaller groups -- Yavlinskiy's bloc or Women of Russia -- so 
