<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Moscow, Jan 5 (AFP) - Former Georgian President 
Zviad Gamsakhurdia has committed suicide, his wife Manana was 
quoted by Interfax as saying Wednesday [5 January]. 
  Gamsakhurdia's wife, who was in the Russian Caucasus 
republic 
